   March 2002

   *Full Committee Joint with Senate Veterans Affairs
   Annual legislative presentations of American Ex-Prisoners of War
   (EX-POWs), Vietnam Veterans of America (VVA), The Retired Officers
   Association (TROA), National Association of State Directors of Veterans
   Affairs (NASDVA) and AMVETS
   DATE/TIME/PLACE: March 20 (Wednesday), 2:00 p.m., 345 Cannon

   *Full Committee Joint with Senate Veterans Affairs
   Annual legislative presentations of  Gold Star Wives (GSW), Fleet
   Reserve Association (FRA), Air Force Sergeants Association (AFSA) and
   The Retired Enlisted Association (TREA)
   DATE/TIME/PLACE: March 14 (Thursday), 10:00 a.m., 345 Cannon

   *Full Committee Joint with Senate Veterans Affairs
   Annual legislative presentations of the Paralyzed Veterans of America
   (PVA), Jewish War Veterans (JWV), Blinded Veterans Association (BVA),
   Non Commissioned Officers Association (NCOA) and Military Order of the
   Purple Heart (MOPH)
   DATE/TIME/PLACE: March 7 (Thursday), 10:00 a.m., 345 Cannon

   February 2002

   *Full Committee Joint with Senate Veterans Affairs
