   *Full Committee Joint with Senate Veterans Affairs
   Annual legislative presentations of the Disabled American Veterans
   (DAV)
   DATE/TIME/PLACE: February 27 (Wednesday), 9:30 a.m., 345 Cannon

   *Full Committee
   Hearing on the FY 2003 budget of the Department of Veterans Affairs
   DATE/TIME/PLACE: February 13 (Wednesday), 10:00 a.m., 334 Cannon

